<span id="line1649"></span>
<span id="line1650"></span></span><span>&lt;<span class="start-tag">script</span> <span class="attribute-name">type</span>="<a class="attribute-value">text/javascript</a>"&gt;</span><span>
<span id="line1651"></span>(function ($Nav) {
<span id="line1652"></span>"use strict";
<span id="line1653"></span>
<span id="line1654"></span>if (typeof $Nav === 'undefined' || $Nav === null || typeof $Nav.when !== 'function') {
<span id="line1655"></span>    return;
<span id="line1656"></span>}
<span id="line1657"></span>$Nav.when('$', 'data', 'flyout.yourAccount', 'sidepanel.csYourAccount',
<span id="line1658"></span>          'config')
<span id="line1659"></span>    .run("BuyitAgain-YourAccount-SidePanel",
<span id="line1660"></span>    function ($, data, yaFlyout, csYourAccount, config) {
<span id="line1661"></span>        if (config.disableBuyItAgain) {
<span id="line1662"></span>          return;
<span id="line1663"></span>        }
<span id="line1664"></span>        var render = function (data) {
<span id="line1665"></span>            if (data.status) {
<span id="line1666"></span>                var widgetHtml = data.widgetBegin +
<span id="line1667"></span>                                 data.faceouts.join('') +
<span id="line1668"></span>                                 data.widgetEnd;
<span id="line1669"></span>                navbar.sidePanel({
<span id="line1670"></span>                    flyoutName: 'yourAccount',
<span id="line1671"></span>                    data: {html: widgetHtml}
<span id="line1672"></span>                });
<span id="line1673"></span>            }
<span id="line1674"></span>        };
<span id="line1675"></span>
<span id="line1676"></span>        var renderBuyItAgain = function (biaData) {
<span id="line1677"></span>            if (csYourAccount) {
<span id="line1678"></span>                csYourAccount.register(render, biaData);
<span id="line1679"></span>            } else {
<span id="line1680"></span>                render(biaData);
<span id="line1681"></span>            }
<span id="line1682"></span>        };
<span id="line1683"></span>
<span id="line1684"></span>        yaFlyout.sidePanel.onData(function() {
<span id="line1685"></span>            enableInlineAddToCart($);
<span id="line1686"></span>            enableImpressionLogging($);
<span id="line1687"></span>
<span id="line1688"></span>            P.when('A','p13n-sc-static-list').execute(function(A, StaticList) {
<span id="line1689"></span>                var navContainer = A.$("#bia-hcb-widget");
<span id="line1690"></span>                var navList = navContainer.find('.p13n-sc-static-list');
<span id="line1691"></span>                A.$(navList).bind('truncateList', function() {
<span id="line1692"></span>                    var staticList = new StaticList(navList);
<span id="line1693"></span>                });
<span id="line1694"></span>
<span id="line1695"></span>                A.$(navList).trigger('truncateList');
<span id="line1696"></span>            });
<span id="line1697"></span>
<span id="line1698"></span>            if (window.P) {
<span id="line1699"></span>                P.when('A', 'a-truncate').execute(function(A, truncate) {
<span id="line1700"></span>                    var truncateElements = A.$('.a-truncate');
<span id="line1701"></span>                    A.each(truncateElements, function(element) {
<span id="line1702"></span>                        truncate.get(element).update();
<span id="line1703"></span>                    });
<span id="line1704"></span>                });
<span id="line1705"></span>            }
<span id="line1706"></span>
<span id="line1707"></span>        });
<span id="line1708"></span>
<span id="line1709"></span>    yaFlyout.onRender(function() {
<span id="line1710"></span>            $.ajax({
<span id="line1711"></span>                url: '/gp/bia/external/bia-hcb-ajax-handler.html',
<span id="line1712"></span>                data: 
<span id="line1713"></span>   {"biaHcbRid":"KAD7CT84NAEQ65ZV43K7"},
<span id="line1714"></span>                dataType: 'json',
<span id="line1715"></span>                timeout: 4*1000,
<span id="line1716"></span>                success: renderBuyItAgain,
<span id="line1717"></span>                error: function (jqXHR, textStatus, errorThrown) {
<span id="line1718"></span>                }
<span id="line1719"></span>            });
<span id="line1720"></span>        });
<span id="line1721"></span>
<span id="line1722"></span>
<span id="line1723"></span>    var updateNavCartQty = function(qty) {
<span id="line1724"></span>        if (typeof window.navbar === 'object' &amp;&amp; typeof window.navbar.setCartCount === 'function') {
<span id="line1725"></span>            window.navbar.setCartCount(qty);
<span id="line1726"></span>        }
<span id="line1727"></span>    };
<span id="line1728"></span>
<span id="line1729"></span>    var addToCart = function(params, callback) {
<span id="line1730"></span>        $.ajax({
<span id="line1731"></span>           url: '/gp/bia/external/bia-cart-ajax-handler.html',
<span id="line1732"></span>           data: params,
<span id="line1733"></span>           dataType: 'json', 
<span id="line1734"></span>           timeout: 2000,
<span id="line1735"></span>           success: function(response) { callback(response); },
<span id="line1736"></span>           error: function() { callback({ok:0}); }
<span id="line1737"></span>        });
<span id="line1738"></span>    };
<span id="line1739"></span>
<span id="line1740"></span>    var enableInlineAddToCart = function ($) {
<span id="line1741"></span>        if ($(".bia-inline-cart-form").length === 0) {
<span id="line1742"></span>            return;
<span id="line1743"></span>        }
<span id="line1744"></span>
<span id="line1745"></span>        var inlineAddToCartHandler = function(e) {
<span id="line1746"></span>            e.preventDefault();
<span id="line1747"></span>
<span id="line1748"></span>            var $target = $(e.target);
<span id="line1749"></span>            var $item = $target.parents(".bia-item");
<span id="line1750"></span>            var $submit = $item.find(".bia-cart-submit");
<span id="line1751"></span>            var params = $target.attr('data-order');
<span id="line1752"></span>
<span id="line1753"></span>            $submit.attr("disabled", true);
<span id="line1754"></span>            $item.find(".bia-action-button").addClass("bia-action-button-disabled");
<span id="line1755"></span>
<span id="line1756"></span>            addToCart(params, 
<span id="line1757"></span>                function(response) {
<span id="line1758"></span>                    if(response &amp;&amp; response.ok &amp;&amp; response.ok === '1') {
<span id="line1759"></span>                        $item.find(".bia-faceout").hide();
<span id="line1760"></span>                        $item.find(".bia-cart-action").show();
<span id="line1761"></span>                        updateNavCartQty(response.numActiveItemsInCart); 
<span id="line1762"></span>                        //TODO: add metric
<span id="line1763"></span>                    } else {
<span id="line1764"></span>                        $target.unbind("submit", inlineAddToCartHandler);
<span id="line1765"></span>                        $submit.attr("disabled", false);
<span id="line1766"></span>                        $submit.click();
<span id="line1767"></span>                        //TODO: add metric
<span id="line1768"></span>                    }
<span id="line1769"></span>                }
<span id="line1770"></span>            );
<span id="line1771"></span>        };
<span id="line1772"></span>
<span id="line1773"></span>        $(".bia-inline-cart-form").bind("submit", inlineAddToCartHandler);
<span id="line1774"></span>    };
<span id="line1775"></span>
<span id="line1776"></span>    var enableImpressionLogging = function ($) {
<span id="line1777"></span>
<span id="line1778"></span>        var registerToLog = function (p13nLogger, callOnVisible) {
<span id="line1779"></span>            var featureEl = $("#bia-hcb-widget");
<span id="line1780"></span>            callOnVisible.register(featureEl, function () {
<span id="line1781"></span>                p13nLogger.logAction({

<span id="line1784"></span>                                replicateAsinImpressions: true
<span id="line1785"></span>                              });
<span id="line1786"></span>            });
<span id="line1787"></span>        };
<span id="line1788"></span>        
<span id="line1789"></span>        AmazonUIPageJS.when('p13n-sc-logger', 'p13n-sc-call-on-visible')
<span id="line1790"></span>            .execute(function(p13nLogger, callOnVisible) {
<span id="line1791"></span>                    registerToLog(p13nLogger, callOnVisible);});
<span id="line1792"></span>    };
<span id="line1793"></span>
<span id="line1794"></span>    });
<span id="line1795"></span>
<span id="line1796"></span>})(window.$Nav);
